description: Discharge a Section 106 Planning Obligation relating to Planning Application 59872/APP/2013/3775 (Variation of Condition 4 (Phasing) of planning permission 59872/APP/2012/1838 dated 19/04/2013, to allow variations to phasing of approved development to allow the Boilerhouse and the Material Store to come forward as Phases 1 and 2, and to allow the Veneer Store and/or Record Stack carparks to come forward earlier than in the approved phasing) to discharge the Affordable Housing Scheme obligation.
